Package com.kuzudb

package com.kuzudb
Kùzu Java API.

Kùzu is an in-process property graph database management system built for query speed and scalability.

  • Class
    Description
    KuzuConnection
    KuzuConnection is used to interact with a KuzuDatabase instance.
    KuzuDatabase
    The KuzuDatabase class is the main class of KuzuDB.
    KuzuDataType
    KuzuDataType is the kuzu internal representation of data types.
    KuzuDataTypeID
    Kuzu data type ID.
    KuzuFlatTuple
    FlatTuple stores a vector of values.
    KuzuInternalID
    KuzuInternalID type which stores the table_id and offset of a node/rel.
    KuzuNative
    KuzuNative is a wrapper class for the native library.
    KuzuObjectRefDestroyedException
    KuzuObjectRefDestroyedException is thrown when a destroyed object is accessed or destroyed again.
    KuzuPreparedStatement
    KuzuPreparedStatement is a parameterized query which can avoid planning the same query for repeated execution.
    KuzuQueryResult
    KuzuQueryResult stores the result of a query execution.
    KuzuQuerySummary
    QuerySummary stores the execution time, plan, compiling time and query options of a query.
    KuzuValue
    KuzuValue can hold data of different types.
    KuzuValueListUtil
    Utility functions for KuzuValue of list type.
    KuzuValueNodeUtil
    Utility functions for KuzuValue of node type.
    KuzuValueRdfVariantUtil
    Utility functions for KuzuValue of RDF_VARIANT type.
    KuzuValueRecursiveRelUtil
    Utility functions for KuzuValue of recursive_rel type.
    KuzuValueRelUtil
    Utility functions for KuzuValue of rel type.
    KuzuValueStructUtil
    Utility functions for KuzuValue of struct type.
    KuzuVersion
    KuzuVersion is a class to get the version of the Kùzu.
